data.text:
Highest Rated: 100% The Wicker Man - Final Cut (2013)

Lowest Rated: 42% The Man With the Golden Gun (1974)

Birthday: Oct 6, 1942

Birthplace: Stockholm, Sweden

Britt Ekland was an alluring presence in a handful of popular films in the 1970s, most notably "Get Carter" (1972), "The Wicker Man" (1973) and "The Man with the Golden Gun" (1974). Her best films kept her image as one of the 1970's most enticing starlets alive for generations.
